      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SCROLL UP (8) is long overdue for a win, finishing in the minors at his last four starts, the latest jumping from this same box when second in a Maiden at this track (22.48). Has the ability and looks hard to top. COPPERHEAD KING (1) jumped from the squeeze on debut and finished midfield at this track over 390m (22.72). Has the inside box this time. This looks easier and expected to improve sharply. MIGHTY EAGLE (7) is a Emma Scott-trained newcomer by Tommy Shelby out of Whodat Diva. Start all important and will need some luck getting across from the wide draw. Can sneak into the frame with the right run.",
